            <p>The pedestrian-friendly Sunset Boulevard and nearby streets make it easy to stroll between restaurants, bars, and entertainment for a complete evening out.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Cuisine Diversity -->
      <section class="cuisine-diversity">
        <h2>Diverse Culinary Experiences</h2>
        <p>Silver Lake's restaurant scene reflects LA's diverse and innovative dining culture, offering couples the opportunity to explore cuisines from around the world:</p>
        
        <ul class="cuisine-list">
          {cuisineTypes.slice(0, 8).map(cuisine => (
            <li><a href={`/cuisines/${cuisine.toLowerCase().replace(/\s+/g, '-').replace(/_/g, '-')}/`}>{cuisine.replace(/_/g, ' ')}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        
