            <h3>üÖøÔ∏è Parking Tips</h3>
            <p>Street parking can be challenging in Silver Lake, especially along Sunset Boulevard. Consider arriving early or using ride-sharing services for convenience.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
