            <p>Many couples enjoy exploring Silver Lake's famous coffee shops before or after dinner. The neighborhood is known for its excellent coffee culture and artisan cafes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Related Content -->
      <section class="related-content">
        <h2>Explore More Date Night Options</h2>
        <div class="related-links">
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/silver-lake/" class="related-link">
            <h3>All Silver Lake Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Browse our complete list of {silverLakeRestaurants.length} restaurants in Silver Lake</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/los-feliz/" class="related-link">
